{"tid":2206265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長毛遇襲︱長毛：被告遭中共洗腦「好悲哀」","createTime":"2020-09-17T11:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:18:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81da97ffa8ead11918aee78f47bf869b29a2f126","tid":2206265,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"八旬老翁今年4月16日在中聯辦外以金屬尖鑿刺向「長毛」梁國雄腰窩，今承認襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，惟他強調「我係為大家好，唔係為自己」，更揚言「一個許智峯，一個黃之鋒，兩個遲早都要死」。老翁獲准保釋候判。梁國雄今早原本準備出庭作證，在得悉被告認罪後，便急急離庭趕往高院聲援申請保釋的快必。對於被告稱犯案是要為「香港出頭」，梁歸咎是「共產黨洗腦的結果」，慨嘆「好悲哀」。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄直言：「一個唔講事實、唔講道理的長者，終日以暴力消滅異見，視法庭如無物，係共產黨教育之下的受害者，依家變為加害者。」他又說：「唔鍾意咪返大陸囉，你可以聽聽香港的民意。」<br />\n<br />\n梁直言香港不少「藍絲」都會如此，常常罵民主派人士為「漢奸走狗賣國賊」。他指中共正以發動群眾鬥爭的「楓橋經驗」治港，以《國安法》呈威，包括對快必以言入罪、李慧琼要求教育局嚴懲敢言教師等，「同清算無分別」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/KYNVMH6YFBF7XLDYBWZITVYJOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FKYNVMH6YFBF7XLDYBWZITVYJOI%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOMrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=b0351a81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FKYNVMH6YFBF7XLDYBWZITVYJOI%2F&h=875bc068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/KYNVMH6YFBF7XLDYBWZITVYJOI/</a>"},{"pid":"bb1c5d76eee58d256f4e492f5f71c512b308b7f0","tid":2206265,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868ebbfd93a18cb9ed98f3fa5a411f221c18786c","tid":2206265,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">其實終身大愛蚑患者長毛都唔清醒得幾多囉<im